Package org.presentation.generators

package org.presentation.generators
  • Related Packages

  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    BaseGenerator
    The abstract BaseGenerator class provides a foundation for specific generators used to generate the HTML pages of the timetable.
    DisciplinesGenerator
    The DisciplinesGenerator class is responsible for generating discipline data for timetables.
    FreeRoomsGenerator
    The FreeRoomsGenerator class is responsible for generating data and templates related to free rooms, including their availability and scheduling information.
    HomeGenerator
    The HomeGenerator class is responsible for generating the home page data of the timetable system.
    RoomsGenerator
    The RoomGenerator class is responsible for generating information about rooms and their associated timetables.
    StudentsGenerator
    The StudentsGenerator class is responsible for generating student-related data and organizing it into individual timetables for each student group.
    TeachersGenerator
    The TeachersGenerator class is responsible for generating teacher-related information and timetables.
    TimetablesGenerator
    The TimetablesGenerator is a class that extends the BaseGenerator class and is responsible for generating timetables based on provided data.
